content: Here are many tools for farming made of straw, some old objects.
There are quite a lot of museums nearby, and it seems that Koreans are still willing to showcase culture, technology and history.
If you come here on a cruise ship docked at the dock Coxen hole, when you exit, once you land, go and you will find a lot of shops. This area is very positive on the cruise ship heaven.
I went there so many times, and no one knew there was such a place.
